author: julianfoad
msg: Move a DB-changing work-queue item up a couple of call levels, as a step
towards replacing it with a direct DB update.
(preserve_pre_merge_files): Don't build a WQ item that updates the DB
with the paths of the preserved files; instead, return the paths via new
there's a conflict; let the caller do that.
(merge_text_file): If maybe_resolve_conflicts() reports a conflict, call
preserve_pre_merge_files() and then build a WQ item that updates the DB
with the paths of the preserved files.
